Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍腐於野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆斷於利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之人 且赴黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是朱絹閣下…是朱絹閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下 在你身後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直立而亡的是甲賀的室賀豹馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 怪不得沒有倒下的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然直立而亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室賀豹馬 好可怕的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹閣下 你為什麼在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 池鯉鮒的客棧出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀的…甲賀的如月左衛門突然出現在客棧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐…朧小姐…慘死在他手下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明發誓賭命保護小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐被殺的時候 你又在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我被緊緊捆住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才趁機逃出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找天膳大人和小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使豁出這條命 也要通知你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才這樣茍且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽 朱絹閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 這樣我就沒有遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱…絹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹…閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹…閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀…敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們兩人索性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同赴死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝女聲可真累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,築前小四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被朱絹擁在懷裏 死於美夢之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧的鷹已經飛回池鯉鮒的客棧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎…閣下他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎…閣下——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左衛門閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你現在的樣子大可接近她們 將之置於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有傷口 身上明明沒有傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你殺了小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹 誰在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個站著嚥氣的甲賀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是和小四郎閣下同歸於盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我用你的屍體做誘餌吧 豹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面部被劃爛 容貌難以分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束髮結於腦後 應該是那個叫室賀豹馬的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要侮辱逝者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳把霞刑部曝屍阪井橋的時候 我也很是反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能和小四郎同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱他 不就等於侮辱小四郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他身死仍直立不倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必對什麼人留下強烈的思念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會天膳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 那是絕無可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左衛門閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳確實死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確停止呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們到底說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剷除伊賀的好機會 不可錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 左衛門閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人自東而來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如此深夜人數卻非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福夫人悄悄離開了伊勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為此回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是為介入此次兩方忍眾之戰而來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立即派人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 何人擋住去路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑人物 大家小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等奉德川家康大人之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正加緊趕往駿府
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是想請問你們 究竟是何來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家康大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是你隨便能叫的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀國 鍔隱的鄉士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你是伊賀鍔隱的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們退下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你們就是解除了和服部家的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正與甲賀交戰的伊賀之人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍家世子竹千代少爺的乳母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的名字可是朧和朱絹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀阿幻引以為傲地列出十名忍者的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽家康大人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是為了竹千代少爺而選出的重要人才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這具男人的屍體是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甲賀卍谷名叫室賀豹馬的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甲賀的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 伊賀女子 你的同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他伊賀人在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰之約解除尚且數日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您剛才所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為竹千代少爺而選出的重要人才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是何意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知個中緣由就和甲賀人交戰至今？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的戰鬥負有何等重大的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福夫人之事 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽之任之的話 也許會無端起浪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰相反
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是為了避免無端起浪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才決定放任阿福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福曾經是稻葉佐渡守的後妻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道丈夫偷藏的小妾生下子嗣後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁千方百計要她接納那對母子的丈夫不在之時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝接他們母子進家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻突然痛下殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後若無其事地乘轎揚長而去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是越壓越容易頭腦發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一口氣掙扎反抗的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任她去才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而不會掀起什麼波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響八郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個第四代半藏正廣可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使阿福試圖耍什麼小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在忍者相爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為第三者的普通人 又能造成什麼影響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無上的榮譽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們跟我一起去駿府吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請務必隨我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了竹千代少爺 絕對不能讓她們死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 絕對不會虧待你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與服部家的協定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩族不戰的戒律已解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 在下不好爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知為何而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 在下即刻啟程前往駿府
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向家康大人或服部大人問清此舉用意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去駿府
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 不能就這麼放任甲賀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 當然不能這樣放任甲賀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能讓你們死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 也許現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先做好朧小姐一個人也能到駿府的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了駿府 就能見到家康大人和服部大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 即使豁出這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要再次締結不戰之約
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場忍法之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟是為了決定德川家繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太"有趣"了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄暮中的夕暮橋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜等待的女子身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕裂弔唁之霧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬千利刃穿透玲瓏之心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄於一捧因緣的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇敵中所見之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿延水際的是赤色綢絹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Basilisk 甲賀忍法帖

